title: PT300RETRORED | '50s-Style Electric Spiral Twister & Peeler
description: At Nostalgia Electrics, every day's a party! We manufacture an extensive line of novelty kitchen electrics that blend innovative technology with old fashioned family fun. The ’50s-Style Electric Spiral Twister & Peeler includes cutting blades that work great on a variety of vegetables and fruit, so you can enjoy potatoes, apples, zucchini, and more. Enjoy a multitude of peeled, spiraled and shredded healthy snacks the whole family will enjoy!
